column3: Ah, adventurer, you couldn't have come at a better time! The preparations for restoring the ward are in place, I'm pleased to report, and with our practiced efficiency, we've established a base camp on practically the doorstep of the Students' headquarters!

Now, in keeping with tradition, the region in which the camp lies has been given a name: Hydatos, a reference to its watery disposition. Gods willing, this will be last corner of the island that the expedition will need to contend with.
But without further ado, let me know when you are ready to head over. Mistress Krile is very keen to resume her efforts with your help!
You now have access to the Forbidden Land, Eureka Hydatos. Like Anemos, Pagos, and Pyros, Hydatos can be explored in parties of up to eight players, or solo.
To embark on your journey to Hydatos, speak with Rodney at Pier #1 in Kugane.

Please be advised that all excursions into <Sheet(ContentFinderCondition,IntegerParameter(2),43)/>, are item level synced. Gear exceeding an item level of <Sheet(ContentFinderCondition,IntegerParameter(1),20)/> will be adjusted.
